title: Exodus Wallet Latest Release 1.41.0 Multi-Crypto
description:
Exodus wraps solid engineering inside beautiful design. We poured our hearts into every detail, from pixel-perfect icons to subtle sounds, making a blockchain asset experience that "just works for normal people". Our goal: Remove the geek requirement to use digital assets and make design a priority - we think it shows.

Wallet
Exodus now has additional safety checks for file integrity on launch. If any type of file corruption is detected, Exodus attempts to auto-repair the files. This helps users who experience hard drive corruption issues or unexpected power failures wile using Exodus.
Exodus notifies you if you are sending all your Ethereum and have Ethereum-powered assets (sometimes called ERC20).
Optimized Ethereum and Ethereum Classic gas prices.
Exchange
Improved exchange tracking for delayed exchanges caused by overloaded network traffic
